Title: Healthgenie Cardiology SS Double Diaphgram HG-403G Acoustic Stethoscope
Description: Healthgenie Cardiology SS double diaphragm is designed ergonomically to ensure comfort and ease for both the doctor and the patient. It is specially designed for cardiology and pulmonary related examination. The conical shaped chest piece is made from high quality stainless steel along with the stethoscope's body. It delivers accurate auscultation of heart, lung, chest, etc. The double diaphragm aids in accentuating the sounds. With its high acoustic integrity and clarity, it provides you with uninterrupted monitoring. Thus, it gives a flawless performance. The heavy duty PVC tubing ensures durability. The soft ear tips enable you to use the stethoscope for a prolonged period. It is intact and does not fall off during use and prevents any sort of ear damage due to high frequency sounds. It's functions are: increasing the amplitude of vibrations of the organs; thereby increasing the clarity, reducing sound transmission loss of energy during check-up, etc. WARRANTY: Healthgenie offers a 1 year warranty. For activation of your warranty period you need to login to Healthgenie's site and register yourself.

Title: Vera Wang Bouquet EDP  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: For the woman who dreams of making her charismatic entrance even more joyous, the celebrated house of Vera Wang proudly presents the luxury perfume - Bouquet. Delightfully floral and feminine, this Eau de Parfum was created to be the ideal scent to accompany the perfect wedding gown. The ultimate expression of flowers and fragrance, Bouquet is nothing short of magical. With the first whiff, you are treated to the sweet citrus hint of sicilian bergamot mixed with the strong smell of black currant leaves. This alluring waft is followed by the heart note that is an infusion of musky hints of white narcissus and luscious honeysuckle. Finally, the base note delivers a symphony of aromas that comprises of soothingly fresh lavender accords, deep musk, moroccan cedarwood and earthy hints of white orris roots. The combination of floral and woody accords lift your spirits with its refreshing scent. You can wear this fragrance at any time and get enraptured in its pleasing air. This enchanting perfume is encased in a dainty pyramidal shaped bottle that is subtly reminiscent of the delicate pleats of a wedding gown. The fresh and minty green colour of the perfume, radiates through the glass bottle and looks as beautiful as it smells fragrant. A spritz of Vera Wang Bouquet and you can transform yourself into a truly captivating bride.

Title: Veet Naturals Hair Removal Cream Normal To Dry Skin
Description: Loaded with the moisturizing benefits of antioxidant and nutrient-rich ingredients like Natural Papaya Extracts, Carotenes, Vitamin C, Flavonoids, Vitamin B, Folate, and Papain, this Veet Naturals hair removal cream is the perfect product for you if you have normal to dry skin. Moisturizes and brightens Rich in nutrients and antioxidants, this hair removal cream is soothing when applied. Its creamy texture allows it to tone and moisturize the skin, giving you a glow that’s supple and nourished. Effectively removes stubborn hair Lightly-scented and rich in texture, this hair removal cream works close to the skin to remove stubborn hair from the roots. How To Use: Evenly spread the cream on your skin, coating the hairs completely, using the curved part of the spatula. After 3 minutes, use the spatula to gently remove a small area of the cream to see if the hair comes off easily. If it does, remove the rest of the cream. If your hair is stubborn, you can leave the cream on for up to 6 minutes in total, not longer than that. Thoroughly rinse your skin with water to wash away the hair completely, and then pat dry. Precautions: Please read and retain the outer packaging that has full precautions and directions for use. The application time should NOT exceed 6 minutes. This product is suitable for use on legs, arms, underarms and bikini line. This product is NOT suitable for use on the head, face, eyes, nose, ears, around the anus, genitals and nipples. Do not use this product on varicose veins, scars, moles, spotty, broken, irritated or sunburnt skin. Avoid use if your skin has had an adverse reaction to hair removal creams in the past.  Please give a gap of at least 72 hours between hair removal sessions. If you are taking medication which can affect skin, or if you suffer from any skin-related disorder, please consult your doctor before using this product. Before every use, test your skin’s reaction to the product by using it on a small area. If there is no adverse reaction after 24 hours, you may continue to use it. If you experience any smarting/tingling sensation while using the product, remove it immediately and rinse thoroughly with cold water. If a burning sensation persists, please seek medical advice. Avoid scratching the skin where the product has been used. Please wait 24 hours before using antiperspirants, perfumed products and artificial tanning equipment, or swimming or sunbathing. Please keep the product out of reach of children. In case of ingestion, please seek immediate medical advice and produce the outer packaging of the product. The product should not come in contact with eyes, but if it does, rinse with plenty of water and seek medical advice immediately.

Title: UNI Kojic Whitening Beauty Soap(135 g)
Description: UNI Kojic Whitening Beauty Soap – 135gm:What is Kojic Soap?•Kojic acid is a naturally occurring antibacterial and antifungal substance found in certain fungi and plant •sources like rice wine by product and mushroom plans. Kojic acid is commonly used in skin care cosmetic products to lighten hyperpigmentation and darked spots that come other sources, It can be used also for •pregnancy masks or stretched marks and other skin disorders. Long term use of kojic acid soap has revealed significant findings of hypersensitivity, allergic contact dermatitis and other skin irritations.HypersensitivityLong-term use in high dosages of kojic acid can cause hypersensitivity in those with very sensitive skin. According to kojicacid.org, the best way to reduce sensitivity to kojic acid is to use a topical corticosteroid to offset some of the effects. If you develop an allergic reaction, immediately stop using the kojic acid soap and contact a dermatologist for an evaluation.Benefits of using Kojic Acid Soap:•Using Kojic acid soap on a regular basis may help reduce the appearance of age spots on your skin.•The best important thing of using kojic acid soap is that it has antibacterial and anti-fungal properties. It kills all your skin diseases that other medicine cannot.•It eliminates skin discoloration from pregnancy and strengthen cell activity.•It eliminates freckles and other dark spots on your skin.Ingredients:Kojic Acid, Sodium Palmitate, Palm Kernilate, Vitamin C, MoisturizerDirection: Lather Soap into hands until foam appears and gently massage into face for 15-20 seconds. Rinse thoroughly. For body, lather soap directly onto wet skin.
